@Comment:	For the most part , Chi works independently with the magnets , and Mot joins in rarely. It seems like Chi has her own agenda and does not want Mot to help with the magnets , often undoing what Mot has done. While Mot does not join in the play very often , she does comment almost constantly on what Chi does. There is no science talk in this activity.
